<p>Why wouldnt you map out and area..say north to san fernando..south to orange county&#8230;west including El Segundo beach cities etc&#8230;east to say Pomona and just call it Los Angeles and suburbs.There problem solved.No little city councils no silly independent police forces with separate laws&#8230;you will also find more of your inhabitants will get out and explore more of the city (albeit the horrendous traffic) if the surrounding areas where just classed as suburbs.</p>
<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-142643' data-commentid="142643" data-postid="90555" data-belowelement="comment-142643" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to superstud'><i class="fa fa-reply left"></i>Reply this comment</a> </div>
<div class="clear-float"></div>
</div>
</div>
</li>
</ol>
<div class="pagination"></div>

